5_000_000` (0.005 SOL)\n- `COUNTDOWN_SECONDS = 60`\n- `TOTAL_FEE_BPS = 300` (3%)\n- `RANDOMNESS_UNFULFILLED` - zero buffer for unfulfilled VRF state\n\n### Test Coverage (Existing)\n\nThe file has tests for:\n- `initialize_config` (1 test)\n- `create_round` (4 tests covering: basic creation, multiple entries, counter increments, invalid tier, zero entries)\n- `join_round` (5 tests covering: trigger countdown, no re-trigger on 3rd player, multiple entries, duplicate player rejection, max 20 players)\n- `buy_more_entries` (4 tests)\n- `start_spin` (3 tests covering: phase transition, idempotency, pre-expiry rejection, Waiting phase rejection)\n- `claim_payout` (7 tests covering: creator wins, player2 wins, multiple entries, PDA closure, unfulfilled randomness rejection, wrong winner rejection, non-Locked phase rejection)\n\nThis infrastructure is ready for `timeout_refund` tests. You would need to add:\n- A helper function for triggering the timeout refund (likely similar to `startSpin` but calling a `timeout_refund` instruction)\n- Tests verifying refunds go to correct players, escrow is distributed, PDA is closed, etc."}],"totalDurationMs":13149,"totalTokens":40506,"totalToolUseCount":1,"usage":{"input_tokens":5,"cache_creation_input_tokens":15549,"cache_read_input_tokens":24007,"output_tokens":945,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":15549,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
